132
00:06:12,010 --> 00:06:14,080
I used to be

133
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:15,650
someone who entertained the villagers.

134
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,040
They always said I was

135
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:18,190
doing some superstitious nonsense

136
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:19,280
