137
00:06:19,630 --> 00:06:20,590
I knew all this.

138
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,920
So, you... well...

139
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:24,190
These skills have been passed down from our ancestors, well,

140
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:24,680
right?

141
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,780
Those special skills and such.

142
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,850
Now that it has been passed down to me,

143
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,680
even if I can't make them flourish,

144
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,240
I can't just let it be

145
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:31,470
wiped out entirely,

146
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,390
right?

147
00:06:32,450 --> 00:06:34,240
When the ghost fire first appeared...

148
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:36,600
we were indeed quite scared.

149
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,890
But after that shamaness spun a story around it,

150
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,550
people actually started coming.

151
00:06:41,890 --> 00:06:42,960
People from the cities

152
00:06:42,980 --> 00:06:44,500
all like folks from the village.

153
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:45,170
Well,

154
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,350
you should've seen itâ€”

