157
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:49,630
Really.

158
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,240
Everyone, you can take photos freely.

159
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:55,409
Take a look.

160
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:57,090
Take a look!

161
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,760
With more tourists coming,

162
