163
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,450
And that means money.

164
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:04,920
One night's stay costs several dozen yuan.

165
00:07:05,270 --> 00:07:05,920
Usually, we don't

166
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:07,050
eat shredded potatoes ourselves,

167
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:08,390
but we sell them for 15 yuan a plate,

168
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,150
and tourists think it's very cheap.

169
00:07:10,380 --> 00:07:12,240
So, why not make this money, right?

170
00:07:14,430 --> 00:07:15,160
Yes.

171
00:07:16,090 --> 00:07:17,190
Of course, we've earned it

172
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:18,240
