173
00:07:19,230 --> 00:07:20,260
But now our lives

174
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:21,680
have hope again.

175
00:07:21,970 --> 00:07:24,090
The villagers are all making money now,

176
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:24,750
right?

177
00:07:24,940 --> 00:07:26,920
Even if we aren't swimming in wealth,

178
00:07:26,950 --> 00:07:27,820
life is still

179
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,920
getting better and better.

180
00:07:29,230 --> 00:07:30,330
Those who went out to work

181
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,290
have all come back.

182
00:07:31,710 --> 00:07:33,159
Well, I've invited

183
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:34,490
the Fire Goddess here, right?

184
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:35,560
Everyone saw

185
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,480
my skills,

186
00:07:36,630 --> 00:07:37,240
right?

187
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:38,740
They all respect me now.

188
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,840
Fortunes change, you know.

189
00:07:43,260 --> 00:07:44,450
So what happened

190
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,310
between you and He Lin?

191
00:07:50,870 --> 00:07:51,520
That...

192
00:07:51,990 --> 00:07:52,610
was my fault.

193
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,470
Business was good,

194
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,120
so I got a bit greedy.

195
00:07:57,220 --> 00:07:58,830
But I really meant well.

196
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,150
I saw that everyone

197
00:08:00,230 --> 00:08:01,690
was making money from the tourists,

198
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:03,270
so I wanted to ask him to join me.

199
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:05,070
He worked hard all day raising cattle,

200
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,160
yet he didn't earn much money.

201
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,680
I wanted to rent his house

202
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:10,050
and run a homestay together.

203
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,550
I'd pay for the renovations,

204
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,550
