205
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:13,330
fifty-fifty.

206
00:08:13,350 --> 00:08:14,580
Wasn't that a good deal?

207
00:08:15,290 --> 00:08:16,960
He didn't refuse me outright at the time

208
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,120
and hesitated a bit.

209
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,400
He said their

210
