215
00:08:27,890 --> 00:08:28,750
and threw a bottle

216
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:29,680
into their yard.

217
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,650
That pregnant cow got startled,

218
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,080
had a difficult labor,

219
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:34,120
and the calf died.

220
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,400
I felt really bad about it too.

221
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,789
I knew

222
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,080
that the calf growing up

223
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:41,590
might have been

224
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:42,490
their family's income for the entire year.

225
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:44,480
I compensated them right away.

226
00:08:46,150 --> 00:08:47,150
I thought

227
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:48,120
