232
00:08:56,630 --> 00:08:57,850
You know, the customer is king,

233
00:08:57,910 --> 00:08:58,910
so we couldn't refuse.

234
00:08:59,470 --> 00:09:00,450
But when they set them off...

235
00:09:01,910 --> 00:09:03,080
all the cattle in the yard were startled.

236
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,030
He spent the whole night soothing them.

237
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:06,960
From that point on...

238
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,910
our feud was established.

239
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:11,940
Every time I had guests at my place,

240
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,840
