241
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:17,650
Liu Bo!

242
00:09:18,070 --> 00:09:18,700
Liu Bo!

243
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,210
You guys go ahead.

244
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:27,970
What's wrong?

245
00:09:27,990 --> 00:09:29,020
It's the middle of the night,

246
00:09:29,310 --> 00:09:30,530
and you're making such a racket.

247
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:31,840
You don't sleep,

248
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,330
but our cattle need to sleep.

249
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,420
