252
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:37,950
Then you should go back to sleep too.

253
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:38,870
It's not like I'm deliberately trying

254
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,250
to keep your cattle awake.

255
00:09:40,380 --> 00:09:41,080
Customers are king.

256
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:41,960
