259
00:09:43,270 --> 00:09:44,120
Alright, buddy.

260
00:09:44,580 --> 00:09:45,530
Don't start trouble.

261
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,660
Go home and get some sleep.

262
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:49,080
