263
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:50,900
Let's continue!

264
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,640
Liu Bo!

265
00:09:52,020 --> 00:09:52,620
Liu Bo!

266
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:54,940
You're a real piece of work.

267
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:15,950
