271
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,120
I'm so sorry.

272
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:18,000
I'm really sorry.

273
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:18,720
Give me five minutes.

274
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,360
I'll take care of it right away.

275
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:20,540
Please go back inside and rest.

276
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,000
I'm so sorry.

277
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,600
What the hell?

278
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,750
Sorry, sorry.

279
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:33,430
He Lin.

280
00:10:33,940 --> 00:10:34,830
Are you out of your mind?

281
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,270
Blasting music early in the morning.

282
00:10:36,270 --> 00:10:37,320
